cs.CV, cs.MED, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper involves the use of automated segmentation methods on CT images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and medical imaging (cs.MED). The use of joint vertebra-rib atlases also involves machine learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper also involves the evaluation of segmentation results, which could fall under the category of graphics (cs.GR).
